  <m>x+y+z=2</m> and is bounded by <m>L_1</m>, <m>L_2</m> and <m>L_3</m>. Orient <m>\cS</m> by the normal vector <m>\vn = \frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}(\vi+\vj+\vk)</m>. Then,
  <me>
  \vnabla\times\vF\cdot\vn
  =\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\big(2y\,\vi + 2z\,\vj + 2x\,\vi\big)\cdot(\vi+\vj+\vk)
